Package: treeringr
Type: Package
Title: Tree Ring Data Downloader, Parser, and Visualizer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sergey", "Mikhno", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "sergey.mikhno@gmail.com")
Description: Download tree-ring measurement files from the NOAA ITRDB
    (International Tree-Ring Data Bank), parse them into clean metadata
    and measurement tables, and produce visualizations including spaghetti
    plots, mean chronologies, and site maps.
Imports: dplR (>= 1.7.9), dplyr, tidyr, stringr, ggplot2, rvest, httr, tools, curl, duckdb, DBI, parallel
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, maps
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
